":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾多本起家？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3萬"},{"pid":"5b6af9696682f17bdbb27864a9e153352e4c1628","tid":56234,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"568ad4c7a8065da475c28ff750ec39ffdd2f2b52","tid":56234,"uid":30914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:05:44.000Z","msg":"想跟你學嘢 只有好少投資知識 零技術分析 受唔受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ad6cd7766a78074d56de62d880247668381740","tid":56234,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1198d277b94090221b43ac86d7b123eca6e0dea8","tid":56234,"uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾多本起家？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哇 咁少本就玩到？唔係果啲咩binary option掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開頭去左中銀開左個股票户口<br />\n用當年以為自己好獨到嘅眼光買左一隻股票<br />\n賺左一倍 其實係死好命<br />\n之後就試好多唔同嘅投資工具"},{"pid":"07d21c41de4488865d9a95b6f3f1f3a0aa09517a","tid":56234,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b7cfb2ce2077ae27be36c67af56a2632971beac","tid":56234,"uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢十年平均一個月淨賺幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過兩年無收入 屋企人接濟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你宜家呢一刻 由3萬開始 玩到宜家咩環境？<br />\n係咪淨係自己睇書同經驗？ 有無咩書推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家接近破產邊緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做地盤佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係 無錯 靠自己睇書<br />\n如果你係對市場無咩認識 我推介Jesse livermore嘅股票作手回憶錄<br />\n去感受下"},{"pid":"8ea6d846fb0c55a095bc3859801f9216841cd3e7","tid":56234,"uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哇 咁少本就玩到？唔係果啲咩binary option掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開頭去左中銀開左個股票户口<br />\n用當年以為自己好獨到嘅眼光買左一隻股票<br />\n賺左一倍 其實係死好命<br />\n之後就試好多唔同嘅投資工具</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係死好命既 咁你真係有料先可以生存到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家係一個失業嘅地盤佬"},{"pid":"c5f188496a4e056ea0fbc65cb30072e95d2fb504","tid":56234,"uid":69218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想跟你學嘢 只有好少投資知識 零技術分析 受唔受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好話學野 依度好多師兄<br />\n大家傾下計無任歡迎"},{"pid":"645fcf4f5ec3064aa3a0cd9bcac24e5e8cc8b9b6","tid":56234,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24a9f8cbc0f65fb7ae86d58208d0acba865be32a","tid":56234,"uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係死好命既 咁你真係有料先可以生存到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家係一個失業嘅地盤佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 唔緊要啦 <br />\n咁你宜家幾歲？ 30？<br />\n搵小左十年錢。有無咩心得比啲想玩全職投資既人？<br />\n小弟淨係信價值投資 長線 唔會全職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n28歲<br />\n心得就係 相比起其他行業 你會得到十倍嘅成功感<br />\n相對地都有十倍嘅失敗感<br />\n你要承受 唔好做傻事<br />\n我以前有個朋友 輸到有情緒病 啊媽又驚左佢啊妹又驚左佢 <br />\n所以 問下自己eq高唔高先<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"e893d573edf5ca2152e17ecd8b208f730e1af989","tid":56234,"uid":26406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:12:45.000Z","msg":"巴打睇咩炒？"},{"pid":"8d5f39c9cc1aa50c20885b7abdc80547daf67a6e","tid":56234,"uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打睇咩炒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7ebd17a8f12d1eb61c8f7669ba3414b14b41cd","tid":56234,"uid":56511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打睇咩炒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係問你Indicator"},{"pid":"fc8dc1d6d490726bb498d4483de40bf399fa83fb","tid":56234,"uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打睇咩炒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係問你Indicator</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇大勢去到交易點決定都自己畫圖"},{"pid":"13d2ea25626518e20a5b01dfd50b5f3437b42db4","tid":56234,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2dca0b5d9e075253b887360d493cfa959692cbdd","tid":56234,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:45:26.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}